name: Hydrochloric Acid
descriptions: A corrosive chemical widely used in industrial processes, laboratory applications, and water treatment. It is known for its strong acidic properties and is handled with caution due to its corrosiveness

name: Isopropyl Alcohol
descriptions: A versatile solvent commonly used for cleaning and disinfecting surfaces, medical equipment, and electronic components. It evaporates quickly and leaves no residue, making it suitable for various applications.

name: Sodium Chloride
descriptions: Commonly known as table salt, sodium chloride has diverse applications, including in pharmaceuticals, food processing, and chemical industries. It is used for saline solutions, electrolyte replenishment, and as a raw material in various processes.

name: Aluminum Alloy
descriptions: A lightweight and corrosion-resistant metal alloy composed primarily of aluminum, commonly used in aerospace, automotive, and construction industries for its strength-to-weight ratio and durability.

name: Stainless Steel
descriptions: An iron-based alloy containing chromium and nickel, known for its corrosion resistance and strength. Type 304 stainless steel is widely used in kitchen appliances, construction, and medical equipment.

name: Copper Wire
descriptions: A highly conductive metal used in electrical wiring and electronics. Its malleability and conductivity make it suitable for various applications, including power transmission, telecommunications, and electronics manufacturing.

name: Cotton Fabric
descriptions: A natural fiber derived from the cotton plant, used in the textile industry to produce clothing, bedding, and various other products. Cotton is valued for its softness, breathability, and versatility.

name: Organic Fertilizer
descriptions: A natural soil amendment made from decomposed organic matter. Compost enriches soil fertility, enhances water retention, and promotes healthier plant growth in agriculture and gardening.

name: Natural Essential Oils
descriptions: Extracted from lavender flowers, this organic product is used in aromatherapy, personal care products, and natural remedies. Lavender essential oil is known for its calming and soothing properties.

name: Microcontrollers (Arduino Uno)
descriptions: A compact programmable device used in electronic systems for control and automation. The Arduino Uno, for example, is widely used for prototyping and DIY electronics projects.

name: LED
descriptions: A semiconductor device that emits light when an electric current passes through it. LEDs are used for energy-efficient lighting, electronic displays, and indicators in various electronic devices.

name: Printed Circuit Board
descriptions: A crucial component in electronic manufacturing, PCBs provide a platform for mounting and connecting electronic components. They are used in computers, smartphones, and a wide range of electronic devices.

name: Canvas Work Pants
descriptions: Sturdy and durable, canvas work pants are designed for rugged use in construction, manufacturing, and other labor-intensive industries. They often feature reinforced knees and multiple pockets for tools.

name: Steel-Toe Boots
descriptions: Heavy-duty work footwear with a reinforced toe cap to protect against impact and compression hazards. Steel-toe boots are common in construction, manufacturing, and warehouse environments for foot safety.

name: Hard Hat
descriptions: A protective headgear worn in construction sites and industrial settings to safeguard against falling objects and head injuries. Hard hats are a crucial part of personal protective equipment (PPE) in hazardous work environments.

name: Surgical Masks
descriptions: Disposable protective masks worn by healthcare professionals and the public to reduce the spread of germs and protect against airborne particles during medical procedures or daily activities.

name: Blood Pressure Monitor
descriptions: A medical device that measures blood pressure levels, consisting of an inflatable cuff to wrap around the arm and a gauge or digital display to provide accurate readings.

name: Sterile Gauze Pads
descriptions: Soft, absorbent medical pads used for wound dressing and protection. Sterile gauze helps prevent infection and promotes healing by maintaining a clean environment around injuries.
